
## Installation

## For development
    # create a virtualenv & activate it
    
    $> pip install -r requirements_dev.txt
    $> fab init_db
    
    ### TODO generate keys files


### Production Install

- configure a correct domain for site with SITE_ID = 1
  $ epio django shell
  >>> Site(domain="scrts-conf-stage.ep.io", name="scrts-conf-stage.ep.io").save()
  
- configure an email server in settings/prod.py